    <panel_attributes>Prologue:
--
Millenias ago, there was a war between human and monsters of
the continent

Human emerged victory, and taken with them the most valuable
trophy: The Ethereal Shard
The Ethereal Shard contains infinite magical power. 

With this shard, and skill in unnatural magic, the Emperor 
has successfully extended his life for millenias.

Those who served under the King gets their reward as well. 
The higher their rank, the longer they live.

It's almost seems too happy to be an ending. 

...

Because of its rich magic source, 
monsters of all kind attacks the Empire, 
trying to lay their hand on the Shard.

And thus, the Emperor recruits adventurers to aid him in 
the continent conquest.

Those who contributed most to monster conquest will get 
a share in royalty luxury, and a long life.

There was one legendary adventurer, so prominent that the
King himself shared him a splinter of the Shard, who nearly
ended the monsters reign long ago. 

He was slain by the monster king. And the splinter fell into
the hand of monsters.

...

Will you be the hero to take the shard back?</panel_attributes>
