    <panel_attributes>End 1
--
The Adventurer brings the Shard back to the Emperor.
He lives a prosperous life forever after...

--
That is, until magic starts running out. 
You have to deal with people and monsters union. 
And then your magic shard fades its light, too.

-- 
You travel to the capital and take the shard from him.
The shard falls into your hand.
And then, over time, the final shard, too, fades away.
Life extinguish.</panel_attributes>
