    <panel_attributes>End 2
--
The Adventurer learns the truth about Shards.
The monster king is the legendary hero in the past.
He's too tired with this job.
He passes his sword to you, embelled with his shard.
The final Shard that'll decide the fate of all.

--
The Adventurer travels back to the capital for the Emperor.
To kill him.
--

The monster king instructed the Adventurer to bring all
the Shard back to the tree after Adventurer has collected them all.
